message.content:
stand: in the future, I will provide a list of 10 terms related to "concession" without further comment:

stand:
booth
vendor
agreement
surrender
yield
contract
deal
discount
cession
compromise

Concessions often involve the surrender or yielding of something, and can take the form of agreements, contracts, or discounts. These concessions can be made in various settings, such as at a stand or booth, and may represent compromise between parties. The term "cession" itself refers to the act of yielding or surrendering control, power, or territory.
